https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

Cast:
---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada
Nitish Bhaluni / Raj Anadkat / Bhavya Gandhi as Tipendra Jethalal Gada (Tapu) 
Amit Bhatt as Champaklal Jayantilal Gada
Sachin Shroff / Shailesh Lodha as Taarak Mehta
Sunayana Fozdar / Neha Mehta as Anjali Taarak Mehta
Tanuj Mahashabde as Krishnan Subramaniam Iyer
Munmun Dutta as Babita Krishnan Iyer
Mandar Chandwadkar as Aatmaram Tukaram Bhide
Sonalika Joshi as Madhvi Aatmaram Bhide
Jheel Mehta / Nidhi Bhanushali / Palak Sidhwani / Khushi Mali as Sonalika Aatmaram Bhide (Sonu) 
Gurucharan Singh/ Balwinder Suri as Roshan Singh Harjeet Singh Sodhi
Jennifer Mistry Bansiwal / Monaz Mevawalla as Roshan Kaur Roshan Singh Sodhi
Kavi Kumar Azad / Nirmal Soni as Dr. Hansraj Hathi 
Ambika Ranjankar as Komal Hansraj Hathi
Kush Shah / Dharmit Shah as Gulabkumar Hansraj Hathi (Goli)
Shyam Pathak as Popatlal Pandey
Sharad Sankla as Abdul
Azhar Shaikh as Pinku 
Ghanshyam Nayak / Kiran Bhatt as Nattu Kaka
Tanmay Vekaria as Bagha
Navina Wadekar / Monika Bhadoriya as Bawri

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: MUTTON BIRYANI | 3 FULL GOAT ROASTED MUTTON BIRYANI Recipe Cooking in Village | Arabian Biryani
snippet.description: Today in our village, we cooked a grand Arabian-style mutton biryani using three full goats. First, we boiled the whole goats in a large vessel with spices to make the meat tender and flavorful. Then, we carefully roasted each goat on a large tawa over a direct flame of firewood, adding a smoky, rich layer of flavor. After roasting, we layered the juicy mutton with aromatic basmati rice, hand-ground masalas, and traditional spices. This massive biryani was slow-cooked to perfection and shared during a village feast. A perfect blend of smoky, spicy, and tender mutton biryani with an Arabian touch.

it.title: BIRYANI DI MONTONE | 3 Ricette COMPLETE PER BIRYANI DI MONTONE ARROSTO DI CAPRA Cucinare in un vi...
it.description: Oggi nel nostro villaggio abbiamo cucinato un grandioso biryani di montone in stile arabo usando tre capre intere. Per prima cosa, abbiamo bollito le capre intere in un grande recipiente con spezie per rendere la carne tenera e saporita. Poi, abbiamo arrostito con cura ogni capretto su una grande tawa a fuoco diretto di legna da ardere, aggiungendo uno strato affumicato e ricco di sapore. Dopo la cottura, abbiamo guarnito il succoso montone con riso basmati aromatico, masala macinati a mano e spezie tradizionali. id.title: Biryani Daging Kambing | 3 Resep Biryani Daging Kambing Panggang Utuh | Masakan Desa | Biryani Arab
id.description: Hari ini di desa kami, kami memasak biryani daging kambing ala Arab yang megah menggunakan tiga ekor kambing utuh. Pertama, kami merebus seluruh kambing dalam wadah besar berisi bumbu agar dagingnya empuk dan beraroma. Kemudian, kami memanggang setiap kambing dengan hati-hati di atas tawa besar di atas api kayu bakar langsung, menambahkan lapisan rasa berasap yang kaya. Setelah dipanggang, kami melapisi daging kambing yang empuk dengan nasi basmati yang harum, bumbu masala giling tangan, dan rempah-rempah tradisional. Biryani besar ini dimasak perlahan hingga sempurna dan dinikmati bersama dalam pesta desa. Perpaduan sempurna biryani daging kambing berasap, pedas, dan empuk dengan sentuhan Arab.

Vervolgens braadden we elke geit zorgvuldig op een grote tawa boven een open vuur, wat een rokerige, rijke smaak toevoegde. Na het braden legden we het sappige schapenvlees in laagjes met aromatische basmatirijst, handgemalen masala's en traditionele kruiden. Deze enorme biryani was perfect gegaard en werd gedeeld tijdens een dorpsfeest. Een perfecte mix van rokerige, pittige en malse schapenbiryani met een Arabisch tintje.

Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. When Raghuvaran, a civil engineer, declines a job offer from Vasundhara, a businesswoman, she makes it her mission to trouble him. However, he takes matters into his own hands to teach her a lesson.

Directed by Soundarya Rajinikanth
Written by Dhanush
Screenplay by Soundarya Rajinikanth
Produced by Kalaipuli S. Thanu, Dhanush 
Starring Dhanush, Kajol, Amala Paul, Vivek, Hrishikesh, Samuthirakani
Saranya Ponvannan 
Cinematography Sameer Thahir 
Edited by Prasanna GK
Music by Sean Roldan (songs and background score)
Anirudh Ravichander (background score only) 
Production companies V Creations, Wunderbar Films
Distributed by V Creations

snippet.title: Namit Malhotra's RAMAYANA: The Introduction Reaction! | Hans Zimmer | A.R. Rahman | Ranbir Kapoor
snippet.description:
Jaby & Achara react to Namit Malhotra‚Äôs Ramayana: The Introduction‚Äîand this one gave us absolute chills! From the very first frame, you can feel the scale, ambition, and reverence behind this epic retelling. With Namit Malhotra at the helm‚Äîknown for delivering global cinematic spectacles like Dune and No Time To Die‚Äîthis project is clearly crafted to set a new benchmark for Indian mythology on screen.

Starring Ranbir Kapoor (BrahmƒÅstra & Rockstar) as Lord Ram, Sai Pallavi (Gargi & Premam) as Sita, and Yash (KGF series) in a fierce new look as Ravan, the film already feels monumental. And the music? A legendary pairing of Hans Zimmer (Interstellar, The Dark Knight) and A.R. Rahman (Slumdog Millionaire, Roja)‚Äîcreating a soundscape that‚Äôs equal parts divine and cinematic.

snippet.title: Cheli 2 : Kehar Kharkiya | Bebodas | Basant Mundi | Yashika Sharma | Haryanvi Song
snippet.description:
Gem Tunes Haryanvi & Rao Inderjeet Singh Presents "Cheli 2 " Haryanvi Song. Sung by Basant Mundi & Yashika sharma. Starring with Kehar Kharkiya & Bebodas. Music is given by Jaizeey . Lyrics are penned by Basant Mundi .
 

üéß Song Credits :

Title : Cheli 2
Starring : Kehar Kharkiya & Yogesh Verma
Female Lead : Bebodas
Singer - Basant Mundi & Yashika Sharma 
Writer - Basant Mundi 
Music- Jaizeey 
Composer- Kehar Kharkiya
Digital Partner: Gem Digital
Social Media Promotions : Gem Digital
Producer : Rao Inderjeet Singh
https://www.instagram.com/raoinderyadav

Music Label : Gem Tunes Haryanvi
Copyrights : Gem Tunes

Cheli Lyrics :

Yani Umer Teri Face Faqeeri Pyaar Chod Gya Re
Karam Kand Ki Kitab Padh Ghar Baar Chod Gya Re
Ho Cheli Ke Chakra Me Chowk Pe Chakar Na Mare
Reh Dur Naar Dur Pyaar Mne Yaar Rhve Pyare
Ho Kde Dhune Pe Kde Jaila Bhitr 
Dhune Pe Kde Jaila Bhitr Dera Babya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke 

Ho Tere Tantar Mantra Laage Pyaar Ke
Vashikaran Mein Hogi Mein
Meri Sehali Boli Gunda Se 
Khud Kushi Karan Ne Hogi Me
Ho Tere Tantar Mantra Laage Pyaar Ke
Vashikaran Mein Hogi Mein
Meri Sehali Boli Gunda Se 
Khud Kushi Karan Ne Hogi Me
Teri Khtam Se Budhi Na Ghaat Me Sudhi
Dharam Dhyaan Yo Vivdha Me
Mere Upper Tle Ye Dhara Laag Ri 
Re Lagi Se Swaad Suwada Me
Jab Duniya Soja Sari Re
Jab Duniya Soja Sari Hove Swere Babya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke 

Basantiya Tu Jaisa Bhi Sai 
Mei Usi Hi Ban Ke Reh Lungi
Tne Pyaar Pyur Ka Na Bera
Mei Bina Pyaar Ke Reh Lungi
Kharkiye Tu Jaisa Bhi Sai 
Mei Usi Hi Ban Ke Reh Lungi
Tne Pyaar Pyur Ka Na Bera
Mei Bina Pyaar Ke Reh Lungi

Kite Or Tu Jake Yo Gyaan Bta
Teri Yaar Nhi Sunte Prem Katha
Kde Byahe Pache Mera Chakra Me 
Re Katni Padja Tne Saja
Mhare Jaila Bhitr Chale Re Chori
Jaila Bhitr Chale Dahi Paratha Dhabya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke 
Cheli Konya Rakhi Yaar Bhatre Babya Ke

snippet.title: Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice in Borderland: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

As new deadly games return, Arisu, Usagi and new players must navigate even more daunting, adrenaline-fueled challenges.

     ‚ÄúSaaS is Dead. AI is the New King.‚Äù
In this high-impact episode, Gobinath sits down with Girish Mathrubootham, one of India‚Äôs most admired tech leaders, to explore the rise of AI, the future of startups, and what it takes to stay relevant in a world that‚Äôs changing faster than ever.

From the early days of Freshworks to launching Freddy AI, from the AI disruption wave to solving real customer problems ‚Äî Girish opens up like never before. He talks about career lessons, handling challenges, building for Gen Z, and why he believes India is ready to lead the AI era.

üîç Topics Covered in This Episode:
 ‚Ä¢ Freshworks and Riding the Wave
 ‚Ä¢ The Rise of AI ‚Äì A Monster Wave
 ‚Ä¢ Adapting Freshworks to the AI Era
 ‚Ä¢ Why AI Is a Disruptive Monster
 ‚Ä¢ Is SaaS Dead? The Shift to AI with Freddy

‚ú® Whether you‚Äôre a student, founder, techie, or just curious about the future ‚Äî this episode will challenge your thinking and equip you to thrive in the AI-first world.
